HEADWORD: Bottomed
<hw>Bot"tomed</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having at the
bottom, or as a bottom; resting upon a bottom; grounded; -- mostly, in
composition; <as>as, sharp-<ex>bottomed</ex>;
well-<ex>bottomed</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

